  "title": "Freelance Wellness Sales Representatives",
  "description": "<h3><a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"></a><strong>Overview:</strong>We are looking for a passionate and people-oriented Wellness Sales Representative.</h3><p>This role combines consultative selling, client education, and wellness coaching.<br />You will guide clients from the first enquiry to full program completion, ensuring they experience visible results and feel fully supported throughout their transformation journey.</p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong><a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><br /></a></p><p><strong>1. Client Acquisition & Sales</strong></p><ul><li><p>Conduct in-person assessments and consultations.</p></li><li><p>Explain our proprietary wellness program.</p></li><li><p>Present program benefits, pricing packages, and customised solutions.</p></li><li><p>Convert leads from marketing campaigns, social media, referrals, and walk-ins.</p></li></ul><h3><a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"></a><strong>2. Client Onboarding & Guidance</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Assist clients during registration, body composition scan, and initial consultation.</p></li><li><p>Explain allowed foods, recipe guidance, and structure of each phase.</p></li><li><p>Demonstrate usage of our technology.</p></li><li><p>Provide pre-program preparation instructions.</p></li></ul><h3><a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"></a><strong>3. Client Support & Follow-Up</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Monitor client progress weekly (weight, symptoms, questions).</p></li><li><p>Encourage compliance through messaging, follow-up calls, or check-ins.</p></li><li><p>Provide basic lifestyle, hydration, digestion, and detox support.</p></li><li><p>Escalate complex cases to management.</p></li></ul><h3><a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"></a><strong>4. Cross-Selling & Program Upgrades</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Promote bio resonance sessions, \t</p></li><li><p>Introduce optional top-up packages (body sculpting, and facial firming).</p></li><li><p>Recommend maintenance and repeat program when suitable.</p></li></ul><h3><a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"></a><strong>5. Administration & Reporting</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Maintain accurate client records, progress logs, and purchase history.</p></li><li>Coordinate appointments with internal team.</li></ul><p><a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><br /></a><strong>Required Skills & Competencies</strong></p><ul><li><p>Strong communication and interpersonal skills</p></li><li><p>Natural ability to build trust and rapport</p></li><li><p>Passion for wellness, health, and weight management</p></li><li><p>Sales-driven with high motivation and target-oriented mindset</p></li><li><p>Ability to explain health concepts in simple, friendly terms</p></li><li><p>Basic knowledge of health and wellness or willingness to learn</p></li><li><p>Organised, reliable, and proactive in follow-up<br /><a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"></a></p><h3><strong>Preferred Qualifications</strong></h3></li></ul><ul><li><p>Experience in wellness is preferred</p></li><li><p>Training in customer service is a plus</p></li><li><p>Fresh Graduates are welcomed<br /><br /><a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><br /></a><strong>Compensation & Benefits</strong></p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Fully Commission</p></li><li><p>Free internal wellness programs</p></li><li><p>Internal Career growth \t</p></li><li><p>Continuous training internally<br /><br /><br />\t</p></li></ul><p><br /><br /></p>",
