    "description": "<div class=\"col-md-6\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 15px; border: 0px; font-family: 'Source Sans Pro', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 24px; vertical-align: baseline; position: relative; min-height: 1px; float: left; width: 433.625px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88);\">   <div class=\"c-text-object \" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">    <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 24px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5em; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: justify;\">     Established in 1997,&nbsp;<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Body Wellness</strong>&nbsp;is a ladies day spa created to reward and pamper modern women with an ultimate relaxing spa experience in a tranquil environment. Situated in the city area, our spa locations is easily accessible with just &nbsp;few minutes walk away from the MRT station.</p>    <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 24px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5em; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: justify;\">     <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Body Wellness</span>&nbsp;believes that body, mind and spirit are connected and every client is unique. With over 100 different types of therapeutic treatments performed through bodyworks, massages and facials, we strongly believed that our distinctive touch will bring customers an enhanced and healthier lifestyle. You can be assured that our qualified and skilled professionals will provide you with total customer care throughout your entire treatment process.</p>   </div>  </div>  ",
